      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "Even if the minimum figures are accepted, it is obvious that no US or",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "text": "foreign aircraft could have been mistaken. The largest known bomber,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
