      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "and only 1 model of each is in existence. Their size mentioned so",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "glibly in the newspaper is staggering. To grasp their size, the Queen",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "Elizabeth steamship is 975 feet long, the Empire State building is",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
